fetime for absolute magnitudes fainter than about -19\nor -20, consistent with the observed change in many elliptical galaxy\nproperties at this luminosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jan 1998 20:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 1998 20:04:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
